# Equity Reserves Foreign Currency Translation Reserve Amount

## identifier
de1542

## type
float

## definition
Report the value of the reserve relating to exchange rate differences arising on translation of assets and liabilities in accordance with accounting standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=Equity.Reserves.ForeignCurrencyTranslationReserve.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo2.02.00
- period=instant
